item.title: CVE-2014-10065|2024-08-06T14:02:38.297Z -- hackerone -- remarkable%20node%20module
item.description: Certain input when passed into remarkable before 1.4.1 will bypass the bad protocol check that disallows the javascript: scheme allowing for javascript: url's to be injected into the rendered content.
